Temporary Install Instructions
------------------------------

- Setup cosmosis
- cd here
- git clone --recursive https://github.com/cmbant/CAMB
- cd to the CAMB subir
- MATCHING YOUR PYTHON VERSION NUMBER:   export PYTHONPATH=$PWD/install/python3.7/lib/site-packages:$PYTHONPATH  
- pip install -e . --prefix=$PWD/install
